column1: #This file was produced by Open Exoplanet Catalogue https://github.com/OpenExoplanetCatalogue/open_exoplanet_catalogue/blob/master/
# COLUMN system_name: Name of the planetary system.
# COLUMN star_mass: Star's mass in Solar masses (M☉).
# COLUMN star_radius: Star's radius in Solar radii (R☉).
# COLUMN star_temperature: Star's temperature in Kelvin (K).
# COLUMN star_metallicity: Star's metallicity [Fe/H] in dex.
# COLUMN planet_mass: Exoplanet's mass in M♃ or M⊕.
# COLUMN planet_radius: Exoplanet's radius in R♃ or R⊕.
# COLUMN planet_temperature: Exoplanet's temperature in Kelvin (K).
# COLUMN planet_period: Orbital period in days.
# COLUMN planet_semimajoraxis: Semi-major axis in AU.
# COLUMN planet_inclination: Orbital inclination in degrees.
# COLUMN discovery_method: Method used to detect the exoplanet.
